Purpose

This document defines how each Behavioral Signal impacts the 10 Mirror Identity Framework dimensions.

Impact scale:
+10 = strong positive impact
+5 = moderate positive impact
0 = no direct impact
-5 = moderate negative impact
-10 = strong negative impact

